DOM-Document Object Model
javascript is used to manuplate the dom and its element 
dom is object oriented meaning that each node has its own properties and methods that we can go and we can change and we can remove things so we can manuplate basically everything on the page using javascript 
jquary was used to do this for longtime

To examine the Document Object
these will help us to print the info which is available in the tags
console.dir(document);
console.log(document.domain);
console.log(document.URL);- it prints the URL of the page
console.log(document.title);it give the title of the 

sytanx to change or to manuplate 
document.title=123;
console.log(document.doctype);
console.log(document.head);
console.log(document.body);
console.log(document.all);
